 <script>
     function CheckUserName(theBtnID) {
         var sUserName = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl04_BannerPagePlaceHolder_p_lt_ctl00_statictext_OnlineBankingLogInControl1_txtUserId").value;         
         if (sUserName == "" || sUserName == undefined) {
             if (theBtnID.indexOf("Spanish") > -1) {
                 alert("Favor de ingresar su nombre de usuario de Banca en Línea.");
             }
             else {
                 alert("Please enter your online banking username.");
             }
         }
     }
     function LoginToBusinessAccount(LoginBtnId) {
         try {
             var postlURL = "https://sccuolb.sccu.com/OnlineBanking/Login.aspx";
             if (LoginBtnId == document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl04_BannerPagePlaceHolder_p_lt_ctl00_statictext_OnlineBankingLogInControl1_btnSpanishLogin").id) {
                 var cookieName = 'SCCU_UserPrefs';
                 var cookieValue = 'DefaultLanguage=es';
                 document.cookie = cookieName + "=" + cookieValue + ";domain=.sccu.com;path=/";
                 postlURL += "?language=es-MX";
             }
             else if (LoginBtnId == document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl04_BannerPagePlaceHolder_p_lt_ctl00_statictext_OnlineBankingLogInControl1_btnLogin").id) {
                 var cookieName = 'SCCU_UserPrefs';
                 var cookieValue = 'DefaultLanguage=en';
                 document.cookie = cookieName + "=" + cookieValue + ";domain=.sccu.com;path=/";
                 postlURL += "?language=en-US";
             }

             //("LoginToBusinessAccount: " + postlURL);
             var windowName = randString(3);
             var sData;
             var formID = "loginform";
             var sUserName = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl04_BannerPagePlaceHolder_p_lt_ctl00_statictext_OnlineBankingLogInControl1_txtUserId").value;
             //var sPassword = document.getElementById("= txtPassword.ClientID ").value;

             alert(postlURL);
             sData = "<form name='loginform' id='loginform' action='" + postlURL + "'>";
             sData += "<label> Username <input type=\"text\" name=\"LoginName\" value=\"" + sUserName + "\" tabindex=\"1\"/></label>";
             //sData += "<label> Password <input type=\"password\" name=\"Password\" value=\"" + sPassword + "\" tabindex=\"2\"/></label>";
             sData += "<input type=\"submit\"  value=\"Login\"  tabindex=\"3\"/>";
             sData += "<input type=\"submit\"  value=\"Acceso\"  tabindex=\"4\"/>";
             sData += "<input id=\"TestJavaScript\" type=\"hidden\" name=\"TestJavaScript\"/>";
             sData = sData + "</form>";
             sData = sData + "<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">";
             sData += "document.getElementById(\"TestJavaScript\").value=\"OK\";";
             sData += "var noCookieIndex = document.cookie.indexOf(\"TestCookie\");";

             sData += "if (noCookieIndex == -1 )";
             sData += "{ document.getElementById(\"TestJavaScript\").value=\"NOCOOKIE\"; }";
             sData += " document.getElementById(\"" + formID + "\").submit();</sc" + "ript>";

             jQuery("#loginfrm").html(sData);
             //             OpenWindow = window.open("", windowName);
             //             OpenWindow.document.write(sData);
             //             OpenWindow.document.close();
             return false;
         }
         catch (err) { alert("error:" + err);
         }
         //OpenWindow.document.close()
     }

     /**
     * Function generates a random string for use in unique IDs, etc
     *
     * @param <int> n - The length of the string
     */
     function randString(n) {
         if (!n) {
             n = 5;
         }

         var text = '';
         var possible = 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789';

         for (var i = 0; i < n; i++) {
             text += possible.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random() * possible.length));
         }

         return text;
     }
 </script>
